Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.38,0:01:38.29,ts,x-lang:ja,0,0,0,karaoke,身騰手なのが世の常だ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.38,0:01:38.29,ts,x-lang:ru,0,0,0,karaoke,Пропитаны, как и весь мир, лишь эгоизмом!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.38,0:01:38.29,ts,x-lang:ko,0,0,0,karaoke,본데없음이 이승의 미립 아니던가
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.38,0:01:38.29,ts,x-lang:en,0,0,0,karaoke,Self-indulgence be the world's principle?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.38,0:01:38.29,ts,x-lang:zh-Hant,0,0,0,karaoke,自我放縱才是世間真理嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.38,0:01:38.29,ts,,0,0,0,karaoke,自我放纵成了当世的常态
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.38,0:01:38.29,roma,____,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k9}mi {\k11}ga {\k9}t{\k19}te {\k22}na {\k21}no {\k22}ga {\k15}yo {\k25}no {\k15}{\k26}ko {\k13}{\k24}to {\k20}wa {\k18}ri {\k22}ka
