Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.89,0:02:03.13,ts,x-lang:en,0,0,0,karaoke,Unlivable, this place, the ephemeral - from it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.89,0:02:03.13,ts,x-lang:zh-Hant,0,0,0,karaoke,自難以生存的此處、自浮世
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.89,0:02:03.13,ts,,0,0,0,karaoke,仿佛要从不论怎么活都很辛苦的浮世 解放出来
