Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:10.18,ts,x-lang:en,0,0,0,karaoke,Crazes then fades, should this world be so lamented
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:10.18,ts,x-lang:zh-Hant,0,0,0,karaoke,若說此世為行時過時輪替
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:10.18,ts,,0,0,0,karaoke,流行啊 堕落啊 也不知道什么是正确的
