Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:28.60,ts,x-lang:ja,0,0,0,karaoke,雪駄屋町通りをも越えて、先へ先へ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:28.60,ts,x-lang:ru,0,0,0,karaoke,Все любят здешний яркий
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:28.60,ts,x-lang:ko,0,0,0,karaoke,나막신 또각또각　어여쁘다
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:28.60,ts,x-lang:en,0,0,0,karaoke,Rings, the winter sandals - but, endeared
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:28.60,ts,x-lang:zh-Hant,0,0,0,karaoke,腳踩竹皮屐忘乎所以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:28.60,ts,,0,0,0,karaoke,越过了草鞋店的街道 继续往前
